<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= statusCode %> - <%= title %> | CMBM NEWS</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-red: #c41e3a;
            --primary-dark: #1a202c;
            --primary-gray: #2d3748;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --light-gray: #f7fafc;
            --border-color: #e2e8f0;
            --text-dark: #2d3748;
            --text-light: #718096;
            --shadow-light: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --shadow-medium: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            --shadow-heavy: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light-gray) 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .error-page {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .error-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: var(--white);
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px var(--shadow-medium);
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        .error-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, <%= color %> 0%, <%= color %>dd 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .school-brand {
            position: absolute;
            top: 1rem;
            left: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: block;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .error-body {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .btn-error {
            padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .btn-primary-error {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #0056b3 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary-error:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,123,255,0.4);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-secondary-error {
            background: var(--light-gray);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .btn-secondary-error:hover {
            background: #e9ecef;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            text-decoration: none;
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .error-details {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: var(--light-gray);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid <%= color %>;
        }

        .error-details h6 {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .error-details p,
        .error-details li {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .error-details ul {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
        }

        .error-timestamp {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .error-timestamp small {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Responsividade para tablets */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .error-actions {
                flex-direction: row;
                justify-content: center;
            }

            .btn-error {
                width: auto;
                min-width: 150px;
            }
        }

        /* Responsividade para celulares */
        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .error-page {
                padding: 0.5rem;
                align-items: flex-start;
                padding-top: 2rem;
            }

            .error-container {
                max-width: 100%;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .error-header {
                padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            }

            .school-brand {
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                top: 0.75rem;
                left: 1rem;
            }

            .error-icon {
                font-size: 3rem;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .error-body {
                padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
            }

            .error-message {
                font-size: 1rem;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }

            .btn-error {
                padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }

            .error-details {
                padding: 1rem;
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }
        }

        /* Para telas muito pequenas */
        @media (max-width: 320px) {
            .error-header {
                padding: 1rem 0.75rem;
            }

            .error-icon {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }

            .error-body {
                padding: 1rem 0.75rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-page">
        <div class="error-container">
            <div class="error-header">
                <div class="school-brand">
                    <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                    <span>CMBM NEWS</span>
                </div>

                <div class="error-icon"><%= icon %></div>
                <h1 class="error-code"><%= statusCode %></h1>
                <h2 class="error-title"><%= title %></h2>
            </div>

            <div class="error-body">
                <p class="error-message"><%= message %></p>

                <div class="error-actions">
                    <a href="/" class="btn-error btn-primary-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                        <span>Voltar ao Início</span>
                    </a>

                    <% if (canGoBack) { %>
                    <button onclick="history.back()" class="btn-error btn-secondary-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
                        <span>Página Anterior</span>
                    </button>
                    <% } %>

                    <% if (statusCode === 404) { %>
                    <a href="/noticias" class="btn-error btn-secondary-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-newspaper"></i>
                        <span>Ver Notícias</span>
                    </a>
                    <% } %>

                    <% if (statusCode === 401) { %>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn-error btn-secondary-error">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i>
                        <span>Fazer Login</span>
                    </a>
                    <% } %>
                </div>

                <% if (statusCode >= 500) { %>
                <div class="error-details">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> O que aconteceu?</h6>
                    <p>Nossos servidores estão enfrentando uma dificuldade técnica. Nossa equipe de TI foi automaticamente notificada e está trabalhando para resolver o problema.</p>

                    <h6><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> O que fazer?</h6>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Aguarde alguns minutos e tente novamente</li>
                        <li>Recarregue a página (F5 ou Ctrl+R)</li>
                        <li>Se o problema persistir, entre em contato conosco</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <% if (statusCode === 429) { %>
                <div class="error-details">
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Proteção contra Spam</h6>
                    <p>Para proteger nossos serviços, limitamos o número de requisições por minuto. Aguarde um momento antes de tentar novamente.</p>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <div class="error-timestamp">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i> <%= timestamp %>
                    <% if (originalUrl && originalUrl !== '/') { %>
                    <small>URL: <%= originalUrl %></small>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Auto-reload para erros de servidor após 30 segundos
        <% if (statusCode >= 500 && statusCode < 600) { %>
        setTimeout(() => {
            if (confirm('Tentar recarregar a página automaticamente?')) {
                window.location.reload();
            }
        }, 30000);
        <% } %>

        // Logging de erro para analytics
        console.log('Error Page Loaded:', {
            statusCode: <%= statusCode %>,
            title: '<%= title %>',
            url: '<%= originalUrl %>',
            timestamp: '<%= timestamp %>',
            userAgent: navigator.userAgent,
            screenSize: window.screen.width + 'x' + window.screen.height
        });

        // Detectar orientação em dispositivos móveis
        if (window.matchMedia && window.matchMedia('(max-width: 768px)').matches) {
            window.addEventListener('orientationchange', function() {
                setTimeout(function() {
                    window.scrollTo(0, 0);
                }, 100);
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>